About
.entry-header
Torrey Oaks RV Resort sits just off of Highway 17, North of Historic downtown Wauchula in South Central Florida.
Those of you who are searching for an Active Adult RV Park with all the right ingredients for the RV lifestyle simply must come and see our resort. The resort sits on 22 acres and has 232 RV sites with full hookups including both 30 & 50 amp electrical service.
Torrey Oaks features quality deeded lots with lush Florida landscaping in a perfect location, secluded yet just a short drive to the areas best shopping, eating and popular central Florida  attractions.
You will find our community residents to be one of the nicest most fun loving groups you’ll ever meet. Our activities director this year has something planned for everyone. Social and recreational functions for the season begin in November.  If you would just like to take it easy we have a lounge with a complete kitchen area, heated swimming pool, lighted shuffleboard courts, Pickleball courts, a computer/ library room, fitness room with a screen TV. We also have a patio area with gazebos and a built in grill, a billiard with with pool tables, dartboards, and a card table. Our 10,000 sq. ft. recreational hall has a stage, dance floor, bingo board and a full sized commercial kitchen.
Let’s not forget the many activities which await you in south  central Florida including Disney, Universal Studios, Bush Gardens and more.  Locally you can spend hours on the Historic Peace River, and an abundance of State Parks and Lakes with canoeing, fishing, and fossil hunting.
Torrey Oaks has one of the largest amenities package in the State of Florida and on top of all that we are pet friendly.
Come for a visit and stay for a lifetime.
Torrey Oaks RV Resort
would like to invite you to our beautiful Class A and Fifth Wheel Resort. Come stay with us. Enjoy the many amenities, swim in the heated pool and the friendly atmosphere. The air carries the fragrance of orange blossoms and the sunsets are spectacular. Meet our sales staff and find out how easy it is to own your piece of paradise. Book Now 863-773-3157
